name: AIcube
description:
This is the first game I ever made! Not a very deep game as you can see but I learned a lot from it :D

This game makes you mess around with physics, energy and boost to get the max score with your cube. It's simple but not always easy!
The colorful environment is randomly generated and it comes with entertaining music that will make you want to play more.

Game Features:
-Simple gameplay
-Randomly generated levels
-Colorful environment + entertaining music
